title: Install error python 3.8 on Mac OS X Big Sur
body:

Collecting shap

         cwd: /private/var/folders/vl/v_qqb7m90j78c3h1d_dyzx3m0000gn/T/pip-install-o84jijp9/shap_92982187dca64ab296328dcab301bb95/
